text: Candela Sol Salinas (born ) is an Argentine female volleyball player. She is part of the Argentina women's national volleyball team. She participated in the 2017 FIVB Volleyball Girls' U18 World Championship and FIVB Gilrs U20 Championship, and 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League At club level she played for Boca Juniors in 2018 y 2019.
